McDonald's Spicy McChicken: 5.2/10.

Toasted, but slightly smushed bun.  Too much mayo. Lettuce pieces that fall off the sandwich. 

Solid breading/spice. Thin chicken patty. Not very juicy/flavorful. 

Good temperature. Made quickly. Not impressed overall. Wouldn't order again.
